@startuml
!include _yunlink_protocol_theme.iuml
title 状态面与事件面边界
left to right direction

package "Vehicle / Onboard Side" <<Neutral>> {
  component "Snapshot Publisher\n周期采样 / latest view" as sampler <<StatePlane>>
  component "Event Publisher\n关键变化 / sparse signal" as detector <<Control>>
  component "Bulk Descriptor Publisher\nURI / channel metadata" as producer <<Bulk>>
}

package "Ground Station Side" <<Neutral>> {
  component "StateSubscriber" as sub_state <<StatePlane>>
  component "EventSubscriber" as sub_event <<Control>>
  component "Bulk Consumer\nout-of-band content path" as sub_bulk <<Bulk>>
}

sampler --> sub_state : StateSnapshot.*\nperiodic / overwrite-friendly
detector --> sub_event : StateEvent.*\ndiscrete / sparse / high-value
producer --> sub_bulk : BulkChannelDescriptor\ncontrol plane discovery only

note bottom of sampler
Snapshot 用于重建当前核心状态，
不应携带一次性故障文本或告警措辞。
end note

note bottom of detector
Event 用于表达关键变化，
不应用来拼出完整姿态或全量状态。
end note

note bottom of producer
Bulk 内容必须旁路传输；
主协议只发现和授权，
不直接承载视频或点云本体。
end note
@enduml
